{"tid":336262,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人需要設計JJ，頂爛市都做！","createTime":"2017-07-26T09:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T05:07:38.000Z","uid":5322,"like":2,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae92cc399c0732fe7aa6039be79caa5cc1bc20e1","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"事源設計JJ預備緊自己kickstart project<br />\n其餘時間想儲下portfo，賺下飯錢<br />\n<br />\nlogo, business card, brochure, edm, graphric, product, or others<br />\n接得就會做到足，做唔黎就唔會接<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小問題係到幫下眼、俾下意見一樣歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/liredot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliredot&d=wUEGWoDItWUnn4dCXV5yADA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=acced856\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/liredot</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧來吧"},{"pid":"72e9ec9facc2eff9051b9504fe34ac19861b6322","tid":336262,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n<br />\n設計jj（乞緊食）"},{"pid":"251d4b4730538eaa128167ef04aab7f161d62ba7","tid":336262,"uid":24641,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<br />\n<br />\n設計jj（乞緊食）</blockquote><br />\nbtw負評左 因為有你呢啲人做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d81bfb22f047d9243398c57b2582831f0484d9","tid":336262,"uid":55937,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"頂爛市者仆街死，祝樓主比人壓價然後走數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d058b8f602dd8059ad8d07fd23c459f0f1bcd5","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平過人係為左提升競爭力，鬼叫我portfo唔厚"},{"pid":"082822fae6a57e4905e0213f86a1ca2db24cc5d1","tid":336262,"uid":73717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"JJ可以有咩設計呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c036bf52a0b15f8f431d2019423e68b10322f1","tid":336262,"uid":30377,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為幫人設計jj 心諗做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97cd66a6712be58c6645fe6cf84d98ee1e16525","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>JJ可以有咩設計呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可按你要求設計紋身圖案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb010aee59ef1194e18078c844ef4d600d81234","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9866cb9288c72126519be5aab46c09a6f6f545f1","tid":336262,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>JJ可以有咩設計呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可按你要求設計紋身圖案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3741359a5fbd4dddb0b45c00b4e1796fb44d7c","tid":336262,"uid":15298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"R生意先<br />\n<br />\n拍片 剪片可以搵我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda0d592de827a990a3afbeaf36f7576313124d5","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3864ff6908435951e2c3c8c54718c72b91e6333f","tid":336262,"uid":85679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"你寫義工都還好<br />\n講明頂爛事，其實你想點<br />\n<br />\n你無錢定時間多定想搞爛個市"},{"pid":"41ddae2a003586adbcf7d5ce897f755cd6bfd8fd","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你寫義工都還好<br />\n講明頂爛事，其實你想點<br />\n<br />\n你無錢定時間多定想搞爛個市</blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平過人係為左提升競爭力，鬼叫我portfo唔厚"},{"pid":"008e8cac739e949f470b515e85888ab3e1ad255d","tid":336262,"uid":45905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:57:07.000Z","msg":"就係多得你衣種人,先會咁多人覺得設計係一文不值"},{"pid":"00aa0a6737cef7b0b67ac27f04ab1fefee4061dd","tid":336262,"uid":68003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"早排我去見工，有個design manager 同我講，佢有個朋友做graphic design, 22 年經驗， 最近搵工比人開價雞中。<br />\n有時fresh grad 出到黎，比HR 壓價，佢地又唔想無offer, 點都會accept 左。 我做左咁耐，我唔見到人工有咩點加過<br />\n<br />\n頂爛市真心大把人會咁做。但到頭來黎個行業真係搞到好差"},{"pid":"391f3cb56282d8908b211d3d2befe9e0f470b2b5","tid":336262,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"頂爛都做，成個設計業俾你搞亂哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0895e62c0a9b9afc92118f0879f7e8868a307748","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"老老實實大家唔好太肉緊同放錯重點<br />\n<br />\n我一句話頂爛市就頂得爛？大家同業，邊個唔想個市好，但收得平唔等於破壞市場<br />\n<br />\n問心，收得平既有幾多個認真做野<br />\n一味要求平既客又識幾多野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n設計生存空間少，除左港企當我地廉價公仔佬外<br />\n我地自己都有責任灌輸正確觀念俾客，等佢地知道設計既價值係邊。<br />\n<br />\n可能我表達得唔好<br />\n頂爛市大家當招徠好，我唔係要做最平最cheap<br />\n係講緊相宜價錢，接得就會用心用腦同你度，有根有據點解咁樣好、咁樣唔好，唔係單純代筆公仔佬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岀面大把人收你一樣錢，不假思索、隨便岀幾個稿等收錢。<br />\n<br />\n我係想對得個產業、對很住個客、對得住自己，唔係要大家無得撈。 <br />\n<br />\n如有冒犯、得罪哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好歡迎大家一齊討論"},{"pid":"8dc2e82f31214d4d6c41c91975339d8c8cd7003b","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33803c24b6145fb3cba46cdd1d42f22722a6a5a4","tid":336262,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咩"},{"pid":"f358c93f4f26941fbbb5bbda99c046b5dc541615","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ac688f0e177699e4cbe761447f3d1e70eb3bbf","tid":336262,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"希望樓主可以死全家，香港多你呢d 人先冇進步"},{"pid":"a928f9f682d3308b1225b2d355761cbae10049b9","tid":336262,"uid":85931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"無人尊重設計咪你呢種人造成<br />\n自己都唔尊重自己<br />\n有portfo又點<br />\n賺個少少錢無限改喊住做"},{"pid":"e5f0364f2f071b509585a70413ab0c00a3d87848","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望樓主可以死全家，香港多你呢d 人先冇進步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高質留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96634d54f1bbd0cceb006e155f25de19c7df3dc7","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人尊重設計咪你呢種人造成<br />\n自己都唔尊重自己<br />\n有portfo又點<br />\n賺個少少錢無限改喊住做</blockquote><br />\n你點睇到我會無限改喊住做？<br />\n<br />\n接乜做乜係我自己決定既。<br />\n客簡我，我都有權簡客，唔適合自然唔會接。<br />\n唔入流先會來者不拒，又唔識保障雙方要俾人食住無限改。<br />\n<br />\n成個流程由無到有應該係點、改幾多次、大改細改，白紙黑字。<br />\n<br />\n尊唔尊重自己、設計唔到你評論<br />\n收費相宜唔等於無原則<br />\n切忌以己度人"},{"pid":"521926cbe3fa06b334a61a3f0da7e56435ff57b1","tid":336262,"uid":83893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"多得你啲咁嘅人做爛個市<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14f331c4e812d19e3e66762aedd6a0c9c470197","tid":336262,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:58:05.000Z","msg":"值一百蚊嘅野<br />\n你賣五十<br />\n你下次賣返一百仲有無人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100db4a3dd02c5a0372b8d2eeb70227c0640af54","tid":336262,"uid":41643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:02:45.000Z","msg":"負評"},{"pid":"c7a7e909420124dd739cb71fb04845d75e467475","tid":336262,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇下你有幾高質先, portfolio 呢?"},{"pid":"7cf8447b6154fb913abcf480bd056e2d77188ef2","tid":336262,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"老老實實，現實中無頂爛過個市，不要再死全家屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84d6687145c46e24d22bd3cb2b58f7c1dc90927","tid":336262,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:43:03.000Z","msg":"負評 上一頁"},{"pid":"8a3a23fc5110cedc47db30cea4984b04021bfae5","tid":336262,"uid":24339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"40個負皮自己反省下啦"},{"pid":"a37e324c87eb3a2b876129a75a3494b945ebe472","tid":336262,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa